  id: MythicalPlates
  title: Mythical Plates
  author: thunder725
  description: '=-= This module pack is currently in Public Beta. It needs to be subscribed
    voluntarily to function. The up-to-date manuals are available in #mod-creation
    in the public KTANE Discord =-=


    "The rightful bearer of a Plate draws from the Plate it holds."


    Harness the power of the Mythical Plates and defy the very fabric of reality!


    18 new challenges all centered around a mechanic of Void, combined with a cellular
    automaton, a tower defense game, a Rubik''s Cube or a chain of plane flights.


    If you feel adventurous, you can defy the Allmighty Sinnoh and solve 3 randomly-selected
    challenges in a row.

    Otherwise, they each are contained within their own individual Plate module.


    Created by: thunder725


    Includes the following 19 modules:

    - Allmighty Sinnoh

    - Blank Plate

    - Draco Plate

    - Dread Plate

    - Earth Plate

    - Fist Plate

    - Flame Plate

    - Icicle Plate

    - Insect Plate

    - Iron Plate

    - Meadow Plate

    - Mind Plate

    - Pixie Plate

    - Sky Plate

    - Splash Plate

    - Spooky Plate

    - Stone Plate

    - Toxic Plate

    - Zap Plate


    Manuals can be found at https://ktane.timwi.de/


    Includes Twitch Plays compatibility.


    =-= Version History =-=

    =-= 0.8

    - Open for Public Beta Testing


    =-= 0.8.1

    - Fixed Draco Plate and Blank Plate modules not having proper reset buttons.


    =-= 0.8.2

    - Pixie Plate: Fixed Ifle-Sym healing Demons when attacking them if its attack
    stat was negative.


    =-= 0.8.3

    - Pixie Plate: Void now affects player movement during the setup phase'
  version: 0.8.1
  outputFolder: build
  debugBuild: 1
  previewImage: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 3435afec60dddb141ad5f45675da578c, type: 3}
